<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deng Xiaoping Medal Selling Well in Guangdong </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK2104151594 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in English 1318 GMT 
21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK2104151594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Guangzhou, April 21 (CNS) -- A Deng Xiaoping medal 
officially produced and put on sale for the fist time has been 
well received with its sale in the city exceeding 2,000 pieces 
in just one month. 
  The obverse side of the copper medal portrays Deng's head 
and 
the characters "Our General Architect" while the converse side 
shows a map of China and with the characters "Construct 
socialism with Chinese characteristics" both in Chinese and in 
English. 
  The medal selling at RMB 46 is produced by institutions in 
Beijing to meet the demands of the public there and also as a 
gift item on the occasion of the 90th birthday of Deng Xiaoping 
on August 22 this year. 
  An observer here believed that production of the badge was 
of 
great significance not only for its intrinsic but also its 
monetary value. 

