always cared about Sino-U.S. relations. He visited China seven 
times, made important contributions to the improvement and 
development of the two countries' relations, and had the respect 
of the Chinese people. I wish to express my profound condolences 
on his death, and also my sincere sympathy for Mr. Nixon's 
